  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Provides that the New York labor law shall be construed liberally for the accomplishment of its remedial purposes, regardless of whether similarly-worded provisions of federal laws or regulations have been or continue to be construed otherwise."
    }
